How long will you upset me?

144
00:12:06,404 --> 00:12:06,954
Okay!

145
00:12:09,066 --> 00:12:10,526
I won't bother you anymore.

146
00:12:25,820 --> 00:12:26,910
Oh? Tin.

147
00:12:27,250 --> 00:12:28,040
What's going on?

148
00:12:29,670 --> 00:12:30,590
Nothing.

149
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,710
If you want to poop,
just go to the bathroom.

150
00:12:33,460 --> 00:12:34,910
Why are you holding it in?

151
00:12:36,110 --> 00:12:37,230
It's not about that.

152
00:12:37,970 --> 00:12:40,170
What happened?
I saw that you were depressed since morning.

153
00:12:44,040 --> 00:12:46,480
