164
00:13:06,051 --> 00:13:07,271
Is he still sleepy?

165
00:13:07,550 --> 00:13:09,440
Everyone wants to rest.

166
00:13:09,540 --> 00:13:10,470
Working people.

167
00:13:11,110 --> 00:13:13,310
Even when we are not working,
we still want to rest.

168
00:13:14,363 --> 00:13:15,743
It's because you're lazy.

169
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:19,690
Park is sleepier than before.

170
00:13:20,580 --> 00:13:22,110
He's more sleepy now than ever before.

171
00:13:22,430 --> 00:13:23,930
He was so sleepy that he didn't eat anything.

172
00:13:24,590 --> 00:13:26,130
